%h1.center Welcome #{current_user.name}!

%p Give the sample applications below a try. They demonstrate the basic capability of sending and receiving messages between this website and your phone. Also check the the "Behind the scenes" link at the bottom of the page, to see what's going over the wire .

.m-twocol
  .m-left
    %ul.border
      - [:ri, :mi, :brhi].each do |app|
        %li= app_link(app)

  .m-right
    .m-xmpp-status.border
      %h2 Connection status

      .m-xmpp-status-browser
        %span Browser
        %span.xmpp-status offline

      .m-xmpp-status-phone
        %span Phone
        %span.xmpp-status-phone offline
